author: AFRICA-NEWS
title: Dropbox Shares Jump in Market Debut
text:
/ sudan Dropbox Shares Jump in Market Debut 
Shares of Dropbox Inc. rose 44% to $30.20 in morning trading Friday in their initial public offering, showing strong demand for the stock. 
The trading price Friday is above the offering price of $21 a share and up from its initial range of $16 to $18 each when Dropbox kicked off its meetings with investors earlier this month. Shares are trading on Nasdaq under the symbol DBX.
